name: Econo DX
description:
• Satisfaction Guaranteed: If you are not entirely satisfied with our product, you can either Exchange or receive a full refund.
  • Designed for Official use, commonly known as the “Pocket pen”. It’s sole purpose is to give your writing experience in office and school a smooth feeling. Also gives you a professional look for it’s outlook and suitable in Office desks.
  • Excellent Ink Quality gives you a high precision clear writing. Prevents your documents from fading away and so you can save it for years. Very good for school going children and very comfortable to write. A true ballpoint ink pen which will give you an excellent writing experience. This pen uses high quality imported ink, which brightens up your notes and preserve the note year after year.
  • 0.5 mm Tungsten Carbide ball & 7.5 mm tip length guarantees its longevity and ensures better and smooth control. Even after direct fall the tip writes smoothly, which works perfectly for the kids as they trends to break things often. The soft rubber grip makes it easy to hold the ink pen and you can work with the pen for a long time.
  • Refillable Transparent Barrel allows you to monitor the ink level. So no skip, no chance for unwanted ink drop. The ink capacity makes it write longer than the average top branded ink pens. Quick Dry Ink and no smear at all after a few seconds. Perfect for school, office and home use. Works well for left-handed as well.
